Long-Term Treatment with Telotristat Ethyl in Patients with Carcinoid Syndrome 
Symptoms: Results from the TELEPATH Study.

Hörsch D(1), Anthony L(2), Gross DJ(3), Valle JW(4), Welin S(5), Benavent M(6), 
Caplin M(7), Pavel M(8), Bergsland E(9), Öberg K(5), Kassler-Taub KB(10), Binder 
P(10), Banks P(10), Lapuerta P(10), Kulke MH(11).

Author information:
(1)Department of Gastroenterology/Endocrinology, Center for Neuroendocrine 
Tumors, Zentralklinik Bad Berka, Bad Berka, Germany.
(2)Markey Cancer Center, University of Kentucky, Lexington, Kentucky, USA.
(3)Neuroendocrine Tumor Unit, Department of Medicine, Endocrine Service, 
